<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id47a48bb6-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a" identifier="/us/usc/t26/s8003"><num value="8003">§ 8003.</num><heading> Election of chairman and vice chairman</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Joint Committee shall elect a chairman and vice chairman from among its members.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id47a48bb7-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a">(<ref href="/us/act/1954-08-16/ch736">Aug. 16, 1954, ch. 736</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/68A/926">68A Stat. 926</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
